INSERT INTO `c5_news` VALUES ('1', '迪士尼星球大战乐园今年8月开业，预计年游客量提升25%', '核心提示：迪士尼近日宣布加州迪士尼乐园和佛罗里达州好莱坞主题公园中的星球大战乐园将分别于5月31日和8月29日开业，比公司之前预计的夏季和秋季提前不少。', '李海强 ', '迪士尼，主题公园，星球大战，IP', '<p>主题公园两大巨头的较量正式进入白热化。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>迪士尼近日宣布加州迪士尼乐园和佛罗里达州好莱坞主题公园中的星球大战乐园将分别于5月31日和8月29日开业，比公司之前预计的夏季和秋季提前不少。<br/>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" height=\"329\" alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190405/1554436093171651.jpg\"/><br/>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>就在不久前，环球影城刚刚宣布奥兰多主题公园新增过山车Hagrid&#39;sMagicalCreaturesMotorbikeAdventure将于6月13日对外开放，而另一个经典IP打造的侏罗纪世界主题乐园也将在今年取代奥兰多环球影城中老化的侏罗纪公园景点。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>一直以来，两家公司都在密切关注对方新景点的开业日期，以制定相应的营销策略。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>2017年5月，环球影城火山湾水上乐园赶在率先公布日期的迪士尼潘多拉-阿凡达世界前两天开业，而此次加州星球大战乐园确定的开业日期也势必参考环球影城过山车的开业时间。可以预见，侏罗纪世界的开业日期与好莱坞星球大战乐园必有很大的关联性。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>迪士尼此次突然祭出“大杀器”公布新景点的开业日期与以往的套路有很大不同。最大的原因可能是为了分散客流，减少游客排队时间和提升游客入园体验。迪士尼如何改变开业日期策略？未来几年与老对手环球影城的竞争又呈现怎样的趋势呢？</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\"><strong style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\">改变乐园开业日期确定策略</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>与以往宣布景点开业日期不同，迪士尼此次将星球大战乐园内的两个主打设施分两次开放。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>迪士尼CEO鲍勃-艾格在股东年度会议上对投资者表示，两个星球大战乐园中的“抵抗组织崛起”主题景点开放日期推迟至今年晚些时候。他还表示，为了满足人们对星战主题乐园的强烈需求，公司决定稍微提前开放日期。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>将乐园内两个设施开业日期相隔数周（甚至数月）最大的好处可能是分散客流。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>尽管开业时两大主题公园客流会很大，但迪士尼公布这一方案后，很多游客可能选择在乐园全部项目建成之后再去。这样的想法也不无道理，毕竟去一次迪士尼价格不菲，如果分两次成本会更高。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>但迪士尼的宗旨是游客多消费才能获得更多的优惠，此次也不例外。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>根据套票价格级别，持有高级别的年卡会员和入驻迪士尼酒店的客人会优先享受各种服务，而低级别年卡会员一般会被限制很多新景点开业时的游玩机会。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>公司称，5月31日开业那天，只有持除SoCalSelectAP外的迪士尼年票会员卡的游客才可以进入迪士尼乐园，这也是SoCalSelect和SoCal夏季限制时间段的第一天，但Deluxe年卡到6月21日才受到类似限制。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>迪士尼还利用提前预订的方式分散客流。公司规定，5月31日-6月23日进入星球大战乐园的游客必须提前进行免费预约，也就是说，就算有门票不预约也进不去（住在度假区三个酒店的客人除外）。这样，迪士尼在很大程度上能够掌握每日入园游客量的控制权。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>公司采取的第三个分散客流的办法是，佛罗里达购买FastPass+和加州购买MaxPass的游客不能预订乐园内的“千年隼:走私者逃逸”过山车。虽然此举可能引起的风险是，通常住在华特迪士尼世界度假区的常客可能会因不能优先入园选择暂时不住在酒店，但迪士尼会在每日散客入园前一个小时对住在酒店的客人开放。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>迪士尼此次公开星球大战乐园开业日期的方式令业内一些专家颇为吃惊。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>《主题公园内参》创始人兼主编RobertNiles表示，乐园项目还未100%完成就宣布开业日期，这对一向为主题公园行业树立标杆的迪士尼来说，虽然有创意成分在其中，但一旦出现状况，对公司可能会带来负面影响。比如，去年迪士尼加州冒险公园的皮克斯码头因尚未建成宣布开业而遭受外界批评。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>不过，Niles也承认，如果星球大战乐园内后续对外开放的另一个抵抗组织崛起骑乘设施名副其实，且客流管控成功的话，以上不同寻常的开业方式明年以后可能不会被人记住。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\"><strong style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\">星球大战乐园助推游客量提升25%？</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>星球大战乐园与哈利波特乐园客流量的竞争实质上是两大IP影响力的竞争。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>统计数字显示，虽然星球大战在多媒体营收以650亿美元远高于哈利波特的310亿美元，但两者收入差距主要体现在商品销售（330亿美元），后者在全球电影票房收入已接近前者的100亿美元，实力不容小觑。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>据业内人士估计，第一个哈利波特魔法世界2010年在加州冒险岛开业后，该环球影城主题公园当年游客量提升近30%。更重要的是，哈利波特品牌给环球影城主题公园带来的长尾客流效应更加明显。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>比如，对角巷和霍格莫德两个景点帮助冒险岛和佛罗里达环球影城两个主题公园的游客量从1153万人次提升至1975万人次，同比增长71%，这是在此期间平均增速18%的北美其他主题公园难以企及的目标。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>2010年、2014年和2016年在美国、日本多个环球影城主题公园引入哈利波特乐园，并大获成功的事实可能也让率先与哈利波特作者商谈授权的迪士尼追悔莫及。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>不过，有专家预测，迪士尼星球大战乐园开业后对所在主题公园的游客量提升预计超过25%。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>虽然从宣布的开业日期看，此前内业专家预测的开业当天客流达20万可能不会实现，哈利波特第一个主题乐园开业时游客排队八小时才进入园区的火爆纪录也可能不会被打破，但迪士尼这种分散客流的方式从长远看未必不能整体上为主题公园带来最大客流。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>事实上，星球大战乐园只是迪士尼投资20亿美元对主题公园设施更新升级计划的一部分。CEO艾格称，公司目前还正在对EPCOT主题公园进行改造，还在神奇王国主题公园打造创战纪主题过山车。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>据纽约时报报道，迪士尼未来五年或投资240亿美元扩张，对全球五大迪士尼度假区（东京迪士尼为授权模式，不参与运营）的景点全面升级。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>除迪士尼加州冒险公园计划新增漫威主题乐园、上海迪士尼新增疯狂动物城主题乐园外，公司去年还宣布投资25亿美元在巴黎迪士尼修建漫威主题酒店及星球大战、冰雪奇缘主题乐园。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>康卡斯特大金主母公司的支持下的环球影城也不甘示弱。环球影城高管去年表示，过去八年和未来五年里，康卡斯特投入主题公园业务的资金比收购全部NBC环球股份支付的234亿美元还要多。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>未来两年，两大巨头之间的竞争更值得期待。2020年，日本环球影城计划推出全新的超级任天堂乐园；2021年，预计投资65亿美元的北京环球度假区开业。另外，鉴于环球影城在美国筹备新建第三个主题公园的消息传得沸沸扬扬，2021年正值华特迪士尼世界度假区五十周年庆祝的迪士尼肯定也在谋划大动作。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>除了传统的影视和主题公园业务，分别计划年底和2020年推出流媒体服务的迪士尼和环球影城即将在新的领域展开竞争，市值均达1700亿美元的两大巨头之间的“战争”在短时间内不会结束。</p><p><br/></p>', '1', '134', '0');
INSERT INTO `c5_news` VALUES ('2', '外媒：中美有望达成一项协议，美国或取消大部分甚至全部关税', '核心提示：外媒最新报道，据两位知情人士透露，中美双方即将达成一项贸易协议，只要中国能够遵守协议（包括保护美国产品知识产权，到从美国购买相当数量的产品），美国将有可能取消大部分甚至是全部关税。', '吴小华', '中美贸易战，WTO，征税', '<p>外媒最新报道，据两位知情人士透露，中美双方即将达成一项贸易协议，只要中国能够遵守协议（包括保护美国产品知识产权，到从美国购买相当数量的产品），美国将有可能取消大部分甚至是全部关税。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>知情人士表示，近几周，中国官员在与美国官员的一系列谈判中明确表示，迅速取消对2000亿美元中国进口商品的征税是达成任何协议的必要条件。<br/>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" height=\"309\" alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190405/1554436331427899.jpg\"/></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>据悉，目前中美双发的讨论重点在于，是否立即取消关税，还是过一段时间以便让美国了解中国是否履行了相应的承诺后再取消。从美方的角度，他们希望继续利用关税威胁作为杠杆，确保中国不会食言。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>据知情人士透露，作为正在进行谈判的一部分，美国正要求中方不要对美国可能征收的关税进行报复，也不要向世界贸易组织提起诉讼。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>同时两国的知情官员均表示，美国总统特朗普和中国国家主席习近平会面的日期尚未商定。此前，《华尔街日报》报道称，中美峰会可能在3月27日左右举行。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>由于习近平主席需要主持一年一度的全国人民代表大会，并对其它国家进行访问，要敲定具体的签约仪式时间并不容易。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>据悉，全国人民代表大会发言人张业遂今日（3月4日）在北京也对记者表示，中美双方的经贸团队开展了富有成效的密集磋商，“在双方共同关心的许多问题上取得了重要阶段性进展，我们希望双方继续抓紧磋商，达成互利共赢的协议”。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>据悉，亚洲股市随着美国期货价格的上涨而上涨，人民币和澳元在周一的早盘交易中走高。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\"><strong style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\">贸易分歧正在得到解决</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>据《华尔街日报》报道，知情人士透露，中国提出将降低美国农产品、化工、汽车和其他产品的关税，并将从总部位于休斯顿的CheniereEnergy购买180亿美元的天然气。作为协议的一部分，中国还承诺将加快取消外资对汽车企业所有权限制的时间表，并将进口汽车关税税率降至15%以下。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>美国政府一名高级官员周日（3月3日）称，美国尚未对是否取消关税做出决定。该官方员还表示，美国政府内部争议仍在持续，特朗普是无法在协议正式达成前做出决定的。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>上周五，美国彭博社报道称，中美即将达成一项贸易协议。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>整体来看，特朗普及其经济团队成员对达成协议的可能性持积极态度。美国股市已经开始回升，2018年12月是美国股市自大萧条以来最糟糕的一个月份，这预示着全球最大的两个经济体的贸易分歧正在得到解决，分歧不会进一步升级。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\"><strong style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\">“停火协议”后续</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>随着贸易磋商的进行，上周特朗普已经宣布推迟原定的3月1日上调中国输美国商品关税的计划。同时，特朗普表示，作为对他推迟征收关税的回应，他要求中国立即取消对美国农产品征收的所有关税。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>自2018年以来，美国和中国官员进行了几轮面对面的会谈，目前双方正通过电话和视频会议定期接触，以敲定协议的细节。</p><p><br/></p>', '1', '13', '0');
INSERT INTO `c5_news` VALUES ('3', '二消收入占比超60%！东京迪士尼是如何做到的？', '核心提示：东京迪士尼的成功经验对国内有何启示？', '李海强', '迪士尼，主题公园，游乐', '<p>东京迪士尼再次迎来业绩增长的财季。<br/>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" height=\"302\" alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190405/1554436437485105.jpg\"/><br/>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>2月初，东京迪士尼度假区运营商东方乐园公司（OrientalLandCompany）发布其截至12月31日的2018财年第三季度财报。财报显示，东京迪士尼前三季度实现营收4000亿日元（36.4亿美元），同比增长9.6%，其中门票与二次消费收入比例分别为38%和62%。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>此外，东方乐园公司还对东京迪士尼度假区整个财年业绩做出预测。公司预计2018财年营收为5008.6亿日元（45.5亿美元），同比增长4.5%；运营利润预计同比增长2.9%至1134.7亿日元（10.3亿美元）；息税前利润为增长2.8%至1148.1亿日元（10.4亿美元）。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>正在开展的35周年庆祝活动是东京迪士尼业绩提升的主要推动因素。活动从4月15日一直持续至今年3月25日，在此期间，运营商通过组织白天游园活动、各种夜间活动、新增景点等方式吸引更多游客入园游玩。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\"><strong style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\">营收36亿美元，二消收入占比超60%</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>东京迪士尼度假区主要包括主题公园、酒店和其他三大业务。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>2018财年前三季度运营期间，东方乐园公司总收入为3996.41亿日元（36.3亿美元），其中主题公园业务收入3328.08亿日元（30.3亿美元），较去年同期增长10.5%。酒店业务收入同比增长9.2%至551.27亿日元，而其他业务收入同比下降9.5%至117.06亿日元。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>公开资料显示，东京迪士尼度假区2017财年三大营收占公司总营收比例分别为82.5%、13.9%和3.6%。按2018财年前九个月的营收计算，三大业务占公司总营收的比例分别为83.3%、13.8%和2.9%。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>财报指出，主题公园业务收入增长主要是因为游客量和每游客平均消费增加，而这两个指标的提升均与度假区庆祝35周年活动有关，前者是因为成功举办多次活动，后者则是因为活动拉动园区商品销售。其他业务收入下降主要是出售业绩不佳自营餐厅Ikspiari产生的结果。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>不过，从另一个角度讲，将门票收入与二次消费收入分开看待，或许更能看清楚东京迪士尼的收入来源及盈利能力。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>财报显示，东京迪士尼景点及演出秀门票收入为1531.21亿日元（13.9亿美元），同比增长8.4%，商品、餐饮、酒店等二次消费消费总和为2465.2亿日元（22.4亿美元），门票与二次消费收入比例分别为38%和62%。<br/>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190405/1554436438210274.jpg\"/></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 128, 128); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\">东京迪士尼近五年前三季度营收与运营利润数据</span></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>值得注意的是，前三季度，商品销售、餐饮和迪士尼酒店业务增速分别为13.4%、10.1%和11%，远高于门票的8.4%增速。即便在主题公园业务范围内，二次消费收入也高于门票收入，两者占比分别为46%和54%。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>东京迪士尼度假区有76家商店，共有大约1.2万种商品可供销售，其中迪士尼品牌商品3500种，一般商品8500种。在商品和餐饮两大业务板块，东京迪士尼的毛利率都接近六成，远高于公司整体40%的毛利润。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>从更细分的角度看，每游客消费收入也是衡量主题公园运营业务的重要指标。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>受东京迪士尼度假区35周年纪念活动带动，东京迪士尼度假区2018财年前三季度的游客量持续增加。不过，在每游客消费收入构成中，门票部分基本保持不变，商品销售及餐饮消费增加，主要得益于纪念活动期间商品销售增加及游客就餐机会增多。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>美国旅游新闻数据平台Skift研究报告指出，从客源类型上看，东京迪士尼度假区65%的游客来自东京大都市区域，只有6%的游客来自海外，但海外游客在不断增长中；从游客类型上看，与日本整体人口结构类似，游客群体年龄略大，约70%的游客年龄都在18岁以上；从停留时间上看，2006年以来游客停留时间一直保持在8-9个小时。<br/>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190405/1554436438345571.jpg\"/></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 128, 128); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\">东京迪士尼近年来游客量走势</span></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>公开资料显示，在停留东京迪士尼度假区9小时左右期间，每位游客平均消费1.1万日元（100美元）左右，其中门票占比43%，商品收入占37%，餐饮占20%。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>值得注意的是，东京迪士尼70%的游客均为女性。女性近年来已超过儿童成为东京迪士尼消费主力军，超过三分之一的日本女性去过东京迪士尼十次。比如，2013年，《冰雪奇缘》电影上映后，东京迪士尼推出公主裙商品，一年之内为公司带来4.5亿美元的收入。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\"><strong style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\">投资30亿美元应对国内外竞争</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>《2017年全球景点游客量报告》显示，2017年东京迪士尼度假区内的东京迪士尼乐园和东京迪士尼海洋乐园游客量分别为1660万人次和1350万人次，位居世界前25名主题公园游客量榜单中的第三位和第五位。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>不过，在经历2012-2014年较快速增长后，东京迪士尼海洋乐园2015年游客量被日本环球影城超越，而东京迪士尼乐园游客量在2017年也被逐渐赶上。最主要的是原因是，日本环球影城在2014年推出哈利波特主题乐园，极大提振整个主题公园的游客量，2015年游客量大增将近20%。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>这也是东京迪士尼对度假区不断进行扩建或升级的主要原因之一。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>去年，东方乐园公司宣布投资2500亿日元（23亿美元）对东京迪士尼海洋乐园进行扩建，占地面积3万平方米，建成后是现有乐园面积的1.2倍，2022年建成开业后每年预计为公司带来4.6亿美元新收入。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>围绕IP打造新的景点是东京迪士尼一贯吸引游客入园的手段。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>与环球影城的哈利波特类似，东京迪士尼将根据《冰雪奇缘》《彼得潘》《魔发奇缘》等经典电影打造4个主题景点，这些景点将与迪士尼高档主题酒店、商店、餐厅组成迪士尼海洋乐园第八个主题区。<br/>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190405/1554436439301398.jpg\"/></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><br/>2019年，东京迪士尼海洋乐园将推出新增驻场秀SongofMirage等景点。同样，2017年4月公司宣布的对东京迪士尼乐园投资750亿日元（6.37亿美元）的《美女与野兽》主题景点等扩张项目也将在2020年陆续建成投入运营。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>除应对环球影城竞争压力、门票收入降低、吸引老年群体等国内原因外，东京迪士尼大规模投资也有与香港迪士尼、上海迪士尼等竞争吸引海外游客的外部因素考量。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>比如，继去年6月开业玩具总动员乐园后，上海迪士尼今年1月底宣布修建疯狂动物城主题乐园的计划，而香港迪士尼修建中的漫威英雄蚁人与大黄蜂景点也计划在今年对外开放。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>作为全球唯一授权经营模式的迪士尼乐园，东京迪士尼每年将门票收入的10%、商品与餐饮收入的5%支付给华特迪士尼作为授权费用。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>财报显示，2014-2016年，东方乐园公司支付给迪士尼的授权费用大约为2.42亿美元。业内专家估计，按主题公园行业19.2%的运营利润率，迪士尼需要新建营收达12亿美元的主题公司才能获得这份收益，这对不需要投资和运营的迪士尼来说不失为一桩好生意。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>以上扩建项目完成后，东方乐园公司获得的授权期限将从2046年延至2076年，迪士尼看好东京迪士尼未来前景的判断不言而喻。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\"><strong style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\">东京迪士尼给国内主题公园的启示</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>现阶段，国内各大主题公园严重依赖门票收入，二次消费收入大多不足30%，重游率也不超过30%，而重游率超过90%的东京迪士尼在二次消费方面通过混合消费组合方式优化盈利模式的做法，或许能给国内主题公园一些启示。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>首先，克服消费形式机械化叠加，在整体协调情况下对乐园的主题进行混合，使游客的体验全过程在观光、购物和其他消费形式中得以实现。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>其次，优化消费组合模式后可以减少单一盈利模式，使游客愿意购买门票外的其他服务产品，提升乐园盈利能力。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>第三，混合销售模式延伸整个主题公园的产业链，使公园不再依赖门票收入，更多地从酒店、交通、娱乐、餐饮等方面入手，增加公司的收入来源。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>创意和舒适度是东京迪士尼在打造产品过程中十分注重的运营细节。比如其在去年4月推出的新景点&quot;it&#39;sasmallworld&quot;中添加更多迪士尼电影中的人物角色，扩大室内排队空间以提升游客舒适度。再如，在海底总动员骑乘设施中增加迪士尼皮克斯电影中的场景，通过在室外排队等待区安装屋顶，以及调整运营时间让更多游客体验来提升游客舒适度。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>此外，度假区还通过翻修餐厅改善就餐环境、推出度假区手机预订APP、2019年建成立体停车楼、2020年重新设计主题公园入口等措施提升游客入园体验。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>决定东京迪士尼高重游率的另一关键还在于最大程度满足游客的游乐需求。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>东京迪士尼每天有上百个形象组成的“强IP队伍花车”游行。在东京迪士尼花车游行项目里，东京迪士尼选择的大都是长相一般的演员。原因是东京迪士尼认为，过于漂亮女孩的表演会将游客本应聚焦在表演主角米奇和米妮身上的注意力转移。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>东京迪士尼要求所有参与表演的演员必须百分百投入到演出当中，因为来看表演的客人是最重要的，必须为客人全力演出。为了不破坏乐园内的童话梦幻世界，东京迪士尼的配送、物流车辆和人员都在地下通道通行，由电梯运至地上；为让游客有在国外度假的感觉，乐园内的舞蹈演员和外籍工作人员都不使用日语，为的是体现美国文化的“原汁原味”。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>事实上，主题公园等文旅项目的运营，不但考验操盘者的整体规划打造能力，基础服务人员的服务质量也是重中之重。说到底，游玩游乐要的都是体验，而服务绝不是“锦上添花”这么简单，一个温暖笑脸、一个体贴关怀动作、一个体验环节设置……由眼、由耳到心，体验已然不同。</p><p><br/></p>', '1', '7', '0');
INSERT INTO `c5_news` VALUES ('4', '长三角节后招工既“贵”且“难” 普工返工奖金最高飙至五千元', '核心提示：“有些企业的返工奖金已经接近5000元，相当于旺季最高峰的一半水平。”该业内人士表示，以往仅有在元旦前的生产旺季时，企业“抢人”将最高返工奖励推高至万元，但春节后劳务市场属于传统意义上的淡季，很难能够看见返工奖励的举措，这从侧面也能体现出当前劳务短缺的现状。', '卢常乐 詹济玮 金陈怡', '智能制造，劳务工，产业链', '<p>尽管目前招工服务的产业链已经比较完备，但劳务工人不断减少让这个由市场自发形成的招工产业供需链条，正面临着“无米之炊”。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>春节过后，一年又一年的节后用工高峰接踵而至。<br/>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190405/1554436548904537.jpg\"/></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>在全国各地陆续迎来节后返程高峰的同时，长三角的不少制造业企业开始再次面对“招工难”的竞争难题，为了能够招聘到充足的工人顺利开工，不少制造企业不得不使出“浑身解数”。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>在上海松江和浙江桐乡，21世纪经济报道记者调查了解到，当前针对普工的“抢人”大战正在全面升级，成为当前长三角劳务市场现状的一个重要缩影。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>一方面，2019年春节后返程劳务工数量减少的状况更加凸显，致使企业招工成本被迫再度提升。集中体现在今年春节后，长三角不少制造企业被迫在劳务市场用“高价买人”的招工方式。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190405/1554436549658878.jpg\"/></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>另一方面，围绕这一关键市场需求，多年来赖以依存的招工服务产业链也开始出现新的市场动向：假期学生工成为市场“香饽饽”以解短期用工之需，同时往年用于生产旺季的劳务工返工奖励机制，最高飙至万元。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>种种迹象表明，在产业结构调整与更替交叠的当下，长三角地区的蓝领工人缺口正越演愈烈，逐渐成为众多制造类企业生存与发展道路上一条重要阻碍。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\"><strong style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\">郁闷的招工产业链</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>2月25日,周一，21世纪经济报道记者来到了松江区人才市场，5号楼一楼大厅内的简历投放处空空荡荡，并无一人。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>据了解，因为要配合“2019春风行动”在区内各街镇顺利展开，目前松江区人才服务中心每周末召开的招聘活动已经暂停至3月底。在此期间，松江区将在各街道社区共举办17场招聘活动。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>一位人才服务中心的现场工作人员告诉21世纪经济报道记者，尽管松江区的“春风行动”招聘活动还有一个多星期，但目前各街道社区的企业招聘摊位余量已经不足，企业需自行联系各个社区街道询问是否有参会的机会。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>事实上，在此时的上海松江，类似的招聘会正备受制造企业关注。作为G60科创走廊的核心承载区，区域内大小分布着大量劳动密集型的电子加工制造企业，每年春节假期一过，类似的招工“抢人”大战便即刻上演。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190405/1554436549982064.jpg\"/><br/>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>21世纪经济报道记者调查了解到，近年来，以上海松江为缩影，长三角地区的普工“抢人”现象愈发激烈，招人难的市场供需矛盾更是直接催生出新的相关市场服务产业链，以及新的招工抢夺对象。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>“劳务中介服务机构的大量产生，也是近年来企业用工竞争愈演愈烈的结果。”上海罗荔企业服务外包有限公司总经理刘道友在接受21世纪经济报道记者采访时表示，从纵向上来看，当前的招工产业链一般分为两个层级，分别是劳务派遣公司作为服务商是一级代理，劳务中介所和省区代理则是二级代理，前者服务满足于制造企业招工的需求，后者则负责面向劳力市场招收工人。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>在距离松江人才服务中心不远的街道上，21世纪经济报道记者看到大小各式装修的劳务中介门店林立，附近工厂的用工信息实时地滚动在门口的液晶显示屏上，随处可见。甚至一些装修简陋的中介门店更是在门口竖立一块黑板，简单地用粉笔写上招工信息就能够对外营业。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>21世纪经济报道记者采访了解到，尽管目前招工服务的产业链已经比较完备，但服务环节也仅是整个产业供应链的中间环节，劳务工人不断减少让这个由市场自发形成的招工产业供需链条，正面临着“无米之炊”的源头挑战。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>在采访中，21世纪经济报道记者还了解到，为解决短期的用工荒，当前很多招工服务机构正尝试扩大与职业院校之间的合作，通过到职校“抢夺”实习学生带到生产线上工作，以试图阶段性地解决制造型企业急用人的“燃眉之急”。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>“在寒假、暑假的时候，学生工会是企业生产旺季时一个很好的劳力补充，也是当前劳力逐渐紧缺情况下的无奈之举。”一位从事劳务中介服务多年的业内人士告诉21世纪经济报道记者，学生工的劳务成本较低、易于管理的特点，已经逐渐成为近年来招工市场上的“香饽饽”，但其也仅能短期扮演补充劳力的角色。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\"><strong style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\">“高价买人”成趋势</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>不仅只有上海，沿着G60高速一路向西，春节后招工难的问题也在浙江桐乡出现。<br/>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190405/1554436550841326.jpg\"/></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>浙江桐乡经编行业协会会长王振波在接受21世纪经济报道记者采访时表示，从去年11月至今，因订单量锐减，成本提升导致利润空间骤减，桐乡与濮院两地众多经编作坊企业停工待业，导致工人流失严重，直接影响春节后的招工市场。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>“很多人觉得在老家做一份工作也能挣不少了，年轻人觉得做普工还不如去送外卖和快递挣钱多。”王振波无奈地告诉21世纪经济报道记者，长三角地区当前的劳务薪资吸引力已经明显不足，甚至也竞争不过同样缺工的互联网服务业，这或许是当前制造企业大面积面临用工荒的重要原因之一。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>基于此，劳务的成本增长就成为当前不少制造企业不得不面对的问题，间接导致长三角地区的制造业正迎来一次重新“洗牌”。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>21世纪经济报道记者采访了解到，在浙江桐乡，因前期经编作坊企业业务下滑严重停工待业，工人流失严重，不少制造企业正面临既无人可招，又无力提高工人待遇的两难局面。王振波告诉记者，从2018年11月至今，桐乡与濮院两地共有近千家经编制造企业关停。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>而在上海松江，劳动密集型的电子加工企业在面临同样的“考题”时，则只能通过选择增加用工成本来解决企业的用工难题。这其中，出高价买人“备货”和返厂奖励“抢工”正成为核心举措。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>上述业内人士告诉21世纪经济报道记者，今年春节前，部分上海加工制造型企业就预测到了节后的用工紧张，开始通过交“预购金”的方式向劳务中介机构提前预约生产工人。此外，还对春节后能够顺利返工的工人，提供一定数额的返工奖励金，而这一奖励机制通常仅会在下半年生产旺季时才会使用。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>“有些企业的返工奖金已经接近5000元，相当于旺季最高峰的一半水平。”该业内人士表示，以往仅有在元旦前的生产旺季时，企业“抢人”将最高返工奖励推高至万元，但春节后劳务市场属于传统意义上的淡季，很难能够看见返工奖励的举措，这从侧面也能体现出当前劳务短缺的现状。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>事实上，在另一个层面，由此不断攀升的劳务成本，正成为目前制造企业头上的“达摩克利斯之剑”。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>庆业电子（上海）有限公司资产部经理蓝旻煜在接受21世纪经济报道记者采访时表示，逐渐攀高的用工成本，一方面使得劳力市场的观望情绪越来越重，蓝领工人待价而沽的现象越演越烈；另一方面，制造企业受困于竞争加剧，以及前端消费市场的萎缩影响，在成本攀升的同时，利润空间缩小也成为不争的事实。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>“对于当前诸多的沿海地区劳动密集性的企业来说，这或许意味着一次弱肉强食、重新洗牌的过程。”蓝旻煜总结道。</p><p><br/></p>', '1', '0', '0');
INSERT INTO `c5_news` VALUES ('5', 'IP变现鸿沟：国产动漫与主题公园的“可望不可即”', '核心提示：中国正在成为全球主题公园品牌落地首选。农历新年后，有外媒消息称，上海新世界城已获得《火影忍者》官方授权，将在上海市南京西路上海新世界城11层建设一座《火影忍者》室内主题公园，名为火影忍者世界，占地面积达', '杨悦祺', '迪士尼，主题公园，文创，IP变现，超级飞侠', '<p>中国正在成为全球主题公园品牌落地“首选”。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>农历新年后，有外媒消息称，上海新世界城已获得《火影忍者》官方授权，将在上海市南京西路上海新世界城11层建设一座《火影忍者》室内主题公园，名为“火影忍者世界”，占地面积达7000平方米。开放日期等其他详细信息还尚未公布。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>这将是《火影忍者》这个大IP在全球的首个主题公园。虽然此前在日本本土举办过该IP的实境展与快闪主题公园，但固定的主题公园还是首个。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;<img width=\"400\" height=\"413\" alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190405/1554436678645340.jpg\"/></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>文创行业现有的模式是利用IP进行多种形式的开发，与此同时IP在持续的开发中吸引到不同圈层的用户，放大影响力获得增值。主题公园是IP产业链中的重资产，需要强大的内容支撑。国内主题公园经过快速发展已到一定量级，但其中动漫主题公园并不多。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>华强方特在短短十多年的时间中在全国15个城市建起了24个主题乐园。不过，虽然有《熊出没》IP，但在现有的方特主题乐园中只有部分场景、剧场和舞台剧，并不是实质意义的动漫主题乐园<br/>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;<img width=\"600\" alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190405/1554436679131009.jpg\"/><br/>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>近日，中国主题公园研究院院长林焕杰告诉记者，目前方特的《熊出没》动漫乐园已经完成规划设计在几个城市开建，尚未建成落地。一个热门的IP要有人设丰富的作品、持续的内容、好的平台支撑。除了华强方特，奥飞娱乐、长城动漫也在探索中国动漫主题公园之路。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>在国家政策的推动下，动漫产业产值和主题公园数量激增，但其中仍存在“虚胖”的现象，长效动漫IP和有影响力的主题公园稀缺。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\"><strong style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\">IP培育期</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>林焕杰认为，中国的主题公园发展可以分为四个时期，经过了2006年开始的快速增长时期后，随着2016年6月16日上海迪士尼乐园开园进入的新时期。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>继上海迪士尼之后，环球影城的主题公园已在北京开工，尼克罗丁频道在中国的首个主题公园正在广东佛山开建，HelloKitty主题公园落户浙江，并将在上海、海口建设新园，默林娱乐集团希望带小猪佩奇主题公园进入中国。还有乐天世界、乐高乐园、东方好莱坞等其他海外知名主题公园纷纷在中国投建或有投建意愿。<br/>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;<img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190405/1554436680976044.jpg\"/><br/>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>林焕杰指出，国际品牌进入中国之后，对中国主题公园的建设有一定冲击，导致国内一些档次较低、地段不好、管理能力差的主题公园出局。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>在引进的主题公园中，动漫主题乐园占很大一部分。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>动漫与主题公园融合发展模式是动漫产业和旅游业产业融合最直观的模式。动漫资源引入主题公园,进行动漫旅游开发还能克服主题公园对门票价格的限制性,拉长企业的价值链,通过动漫旅游的衍生产品盈利，使现金流更健康。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>林焕杰认为，虽然国内出现了许多主题公园，但主题选择雷同缺乏个性，复制模式居多，没有差异化。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>本土创建的动漫主题公园不少，但许多没有明确的动漫形象主题，如南京月牙湖动漫主题公园、常州环球动漫嬉戏谷、长春多多国动漫主题公园、三亚九龙山动漫主题森林公园、浙江诸暨龙太子欢乐谷动漫主题乐园等。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>国际知名的动漫主题公园一般都是先发展动漫业再延伸至旅游业,当前国内由于缺乏优秀的动漫作品,一般是先建设公园,再寻找动漫主题,边运营边创造属于自己的动漫故事。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>例如常州恐龙园先有主题公园项目，随后延伸至上游主题文化创意及下游动漫与衍生产品制造，陆续推出《恐龙宝贝》系列及《恐龙来了》等动漫剧集和电影以及玩具、礼品等衍生品。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>还有一些是模仿国外的动漫主题。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>江苏省大丰市曾宣布建设以《海贼王》为主题的公园,总投资为5亿元，委托日本木兰创意文化发展株式会社对公园总体形象进行策划和包装，项目招标文件中也指出项目名称是“海贼王动漫主题公园”。但引起版权争议后，项目开发公司出来辟谣称游乐园名称为“大丰港海盗王国游乐园”，与海贼王IP无关。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>作为主题公园规划的基石，国内的优质IP还远远不够，或是停留在动漫和衍生周边产品阶段。当然，国内适用于主题公园的IP不足与动漫IP本身处于用户培育期有关。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>当然，国内发展也不均衡。例如奥飞动漫在PGC领域上，创造了铠甲勇士、巴啦啦小魔仙、超级飞侠、火力少年、开心超人等动漫形象，收购喜洋洋、贝肯熊、功夫料理娘、雷霆战机、魔天记、太极鼠、雏蜂、端脑、镇魂街、十万个冷笑话等多个知名IP。公司旗下拥有原创动力、明星动画、狼烟动画、太极鼠工作室等十余个原创动漫工作室。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>2018年4月，奥飞娱乐出资2750万元，和广东奥睿控股共同投资设立子公司奥飞主题文化科技有限公司，将结合奥飞娱乐旗下IP经营室外实景主题乐园。计划五年内在全国范围内建设多个主题游乐园。其中包括奥飞娱乐与山水文园集团、美国六旗集团联手打造的“超级飞侠”动漫主题公园。<br/>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;<img width=\"600\" height=\"202\" alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190405/1554436680614268.jpg\"/><br/>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\"><strong style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\">规模“虚胖”</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>对于动漫主题乐园来说，成功与否的先决条件是主题是否足够吸引人“掏腰包”。但传统动漫产业“虚胖”问题凸显，我国动漫行业产值在2018年已突破1500亿元，2014年时才刚突破1000亿元，能拿出手的动漫IP不多。林焕杰也指出，一些主题公园的流量数据存在虚报的现象，投资经营数据失实，误导市场情况严重。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>一个IP建造成主题乐园需要很长时间，短时间内决策投资不利于长效发展。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>林焕杰表示，《哈利·波特》、《加勒比海盗》等都是拍了很多部续集才开始做主题公园。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>“国内还是比较急躁，《熊出没》，《喜羊羊与灰太狼》、《超级飞侠》其实逐渐被认可，把IP变成公园是需要一个很长的过程研发。美国奥兰多迪士尼世界的潘多拉:阿凡达世界主题区，卡梅伦导演用了7年的时间才完成，国内主题公园的筹备建设期往往只有一两年时间，所以受欢迎的程度不高。”林焕杰说道。<br/>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190405/1554436681137615.jpg\"/></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>林焕杰还指出，其实也与投资额有很大的关系，国外是投资投入比较大，特别是在设计研发方面，国内的一些项目设施比较粗糙。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>特别是对于动漫主题公园来说，投资成本高昂，但因为受众群体有限，风险或比其它主题公园更大。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>在林焕杰看来，杭州从日本引进的HelloKitty主题公园就做得不好。因为目前动漫公园的主要客群还是儿童，儿童是被动消费群体，有明显的淡旺季。<br/>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" height=\"336\" alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190405/1554436681913197.jpg\"/></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>“迪士尼也不是纯粹的动漫主题公园，因为覆盖的客户群有限，只能是在大公园里面的一个区域做动漫主题。但是如果是整个的话，游客量是支撑不起来的，没有一个公司可以做好。”林焕杰说，如果是全年龄段的主题公园，才能有一定游客量。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>也就是说，虽然有些动漫IP有特定粉丝群体和较成熟的衍生品市场，短期内聚集人气并不是难事，但生命力是否可持续依然不可知。而且，很多大的IP相对孤立，一个热门IP开发的产品难成系列，不足以提供一个大规模的园区需要，可能会“孤掌难鸣”。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>环球影城创意公司副总裁PaulOsterhout近日接受记者采访时认为，如何衡量IP的投入与产出十分重要，关键在于讲好一个故事并且和主题高度匹配，关注叙事技巧，要简单不能太复杂。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>这对于资金预算较少的主题公园是一个方式。PaulOsterhout表示，主题公园未来将多级发展，超大规模和小规模共同发展。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>“主题公园一方面朝大规模发展，在园区内配套酒店和餐饮；与此同时一些非常小的，基于商业综合体、购物商城的主题公园将会出现，未来将很难区分旅游和购物的界限。”PaulOsterhout向记者指出。</p><p><br/></p>', '1', '0', '0');
INSERT INTO `c5_news` VALUES ('6', '迪士尼：对外输出的美国动漫旅游样本', '核心提示：2月18日，香港迪士尼公布的2018财政年度业绩再次展现了迪士尼顽强的吸金能力。扩建计划执行后的首个财年，香港迪士尼全财政年度收入上升18%至60亿港元，EBITDA同比大增48%至14亿港元。', '徐维维', '迪士尼，主题公园，游乐', '<p>2月18日，香港迪士尼公布的2018财政年度业绩再次展现了迪士尼顽强的吸金能力。扩建计划执行后的首个财年，香港迪士尼全财政年度收入上升18%至60亿港元，EBITDA同比大增48%至14亿港元。净亏损大幅收窄至5400万港元，比上一财政年度减少2.91亿港元。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>以动漫起家的迪士尼可以说是美国动漫商业化的典型代表，在文化与旅游的结合不断向全球输出和落地，与日本动漫走出了截然相反的道路。正如上海财经大学文化旅游会展研究中心主任何建民近日在接受21世纪经济报道采访时归纳的：“迪士尼的创意-动画片-超级知识产权-主题公园市场形成了一个正循环产业链，迪士尼主题公园市场对其动漫电影产业发展发挥了引导与可持续驱动的双重作用。”<br/>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;<img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190405/1554436777806007.jpg\"/><br/>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\"><strong style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\">多地推扩建计划</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>在大中华区乃至全球市场，迪士尼乐园都在原有乐园基础上加大扩建力度。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>上海迪士尼度假区1月23日宣布全新的主题乐园扩建计划，全球首个“疯狂动物城”主题园区即将落户上海迪士尼乐园，成为其第八个主题园区，建造计划于2019年晚些时候启动。这是上海迪士尼度假区在开幕后不到三年，继2018年4月首个扩建项目“迪士尼·皮克斯玩具总动员”开幕不到一年宣布的第二个重大扩建计划。华特迪士尼董事长兼首席执行官罗伯特·艾格（BobIger）在2018年11月年度财报公布时透露，后期上海迪士尼还将继续扩张，包括景点和酒店。<br/>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;<img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190405/1554436777578865.jpg\"/><br/>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>香港迪士尼已经开展横跨6年的扩建计划，由2018至2023年，几乎每年都会推出新项目。3月31日，香港迪士尼新阶段扩展计划中第二个项目“蚁侠与黄蜂女：击战特攻！”将开幕，进一步扩展漫威主题园区。公主题材的全新“魔法化妆厅”将于2019年夏季开幕。“冰雪奇缘”主题区将会在2021年落成。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>2019年夏季和秋季，加州迪士尼乐园和佛罗里达州迪士尼的好莱坞影城将分别开放星球大战园区。艾格表示：“星球大战园区是我们有史以来最大的园区，无论是面积和规模、还是试图为游客打造特殊及沉浸式的体验方面，这个园区将对迪士尼产生重大的影响，将推动需求的大幅增长，这也对我们的管理提出了挑战。”</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>从文旅融合的角度来说，迪士尼在主题公园动漫题材落地的选择上遵循的是什么标准？何建民表示，第一是能吸引儿童、家庭与社会大众的眼球和心灵的原则。选择落地的动漫题材往往与儿童、家庭和社会大众喜欢的玩具，动物，公主，奇迹，英雄战队相联系。香港迪士尼新增漫威项目就与创造奇迹的英雄战队有关。第二是能塑造互动主题人物、场景与带动综合娱乐消费的原则。如去年上海迪士尼新增玩具总动员乐园中的胡迪警长，玩具购物店。<br/>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;<img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190405/1554436777114742.jpg\"/></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><br/>CIC灼识咨询执行董事朱悦2月20日接受对21世纪经济报道记者采访时表示，IP的接纳度，尤其是在主题公园当地的受欢迎程度，电影票房和衍生商品销售成绩成为其重要参考指标。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>以上海迪士尼度假区计划打造的“疯狂动物城”主题园区为例，《疯狂动物城》2016年公映后大获成功，全球票房突破10亿美元，中国票房达到2.35亿美元，打破中国市场动画电影的票房纪录，迄今仍稳坐中国电影史动画片冠军宝座，并荣膺奥斯卡和金球奖双料最佳动画长片。《疯狂动物城》是迪士尼动画在中国上映的最高峰，其中国票房甚至超过了《冰雪奇缘》，尽管《冰雪奇缘》的全球票房排名动画影史第一。《疯狂动物城》中的故事和角色相关的衍生商品、电子互动游戏等在中国市场也颇受欢迎。电影播出后，录音笔、公仔、手机壳、马克杯、徽章、抱枕等《疯狂动物城》周边产品成为热卖品。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>同样，美国加州迪士尼乐园与奥兰多迪士尼乐园所选择的“星球大战”IP，在美国受欢迎度极高。《星球大战7：原力觉醒》目前排名北美影史票房排行榜冠军，《星球大战外传：侠盗一号》和《星球大战前传1：幽灵的威胁》也跻身北美影史票房排行榜前十。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\"><strong style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\">推动上游动漫产业</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>另一方面，迪士尼乐园反过来也促进了迪士尼上游动漫产业的发展和生产。北京大学文化产业研究院副院长陈少峰对21世纪经济报道表示，迪士尼乐园既是迪士尼动漫的衍生品，又是其销售载体和展示窗口，非常有助于迪士尼动漫形象的传播，还可以根据游客的爱好再去开发续集或是强化内容和版权。<br/>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;<img width=\"600\" height=\"494\" alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190405/1554436778474784.jpg\"/><br/>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>“迪士尼从不把所创作出的动画形象IP看成一次性消费品，而是作为一个可长久消费、深度挖掘的金矿。”朱悦表示，以动画影视为源头，迪士尼动画形象IP在各动漫产业环节循环运作，逐步积累，从而打造出经久不衰的经典大IP。迪士尼乐园是迪士尼文创产业链上的重要一环，通过影片带动主题乐园的开发，秉承着“创造欢乐”的主题，将电影中虚拟的卡通人物还原到现实生活中，打造一个奇幻的动画世界，为游客营造一个完美的旅游体验。迪士尼乐园为迪士尼动画形象IP热度的维持和提升提供不可或缺的助力，推动其动漫产业其它环节各形式产品和服务的发展。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>从2019年第一季度财报开始，迪士尼的四个板块将变成：媒体网络板块、乐园体验和消费者产品板块、影视娱乐板块以及直接面向消费者服务和国际板块。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>艾格透露，华特迪士尼正在加大内容制作力度，已在筹备中的原创动画内容包括《星球大战》动画系列《克隆人战争》（CloneWars）以及基于皮克斯《怪兽电力公司》（Monsters,Inc.）的系列动画。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>华特迪士尼2018年财报显示，营收594.3亿美元，同比增长8%；净利润125.98亿美元，同比增长40%；四大业务板块中，影视娱乐板块、主题公园和度假区板块贡献最大。其中，主题公园和度假区业务的营收和运营利润在第四季度和2018全年都有增长，但运营利润的增长主要由国内乐园及度假区业务推动。国际市场上，该板块运营利润与去年同期相当，因为巴黎迪士尼乐园和香港迪士尼乐园的增长被上海迪士尼乐园的下降所抵消。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>“2018年中后期，中国旅游市场出现疲软。在此期间，我们采取了降价、打折措施，以增加人流量，效果很好。”艾格在2018年财报公布后的电话会议上表示，相信这种疲软只是暂时现象，消费者信心略有减少，但对这块业务很有信心，以后还会继续投资。2017年财报显示，上海迪士尼度假村在第一个完整财年的营业收入为正数，超出了公司之前收支平衡的预期。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>1月23日，上海迪士尼乐园首次推出年卡，分为“周日年卡”、“平日+周日年卡”和“无限年卡”三种类别。何建民认为，上海迪士尼的年卡，可以更好地将迪士尼可开园娱乐的活动时间与不同游客的潜在需求结合起来，更加有效地利用上海迪士尼的淡季时间，增加经营收入。中国主题公园研究院院长林焕杰近日对21世纪经济报道记者表示，年卡的目的是希望获得一批固定的游客，通过固定游客带动零散游客，同时也是与会员制度类似、通过会员口碑传播的一种营销手段。“迪士尼没有公布具体数据，一般来说，主题公园推出年卡会有一个指标，比如我这公园有1000亩地，我可能一年会卖出两万张年卡，我要确保这批人每年会来一次，一个人再带来两个人，即卖出一张年卡，有三个人去。”</p><p><br/></p>', '1', '0', '0');
INSERT INTO `c5_news` VALUES ('7', '动漫产业中美日“三国杀”', '核心提示：一些主题公园的流量数据存在虚报的现象，投资经营数据失实，误导市场情况严重。', '杨悦祺', '动漫，主题公园', '<p>中国正在成为全球主题公园品牌落地“首选”。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>农历新年后，有外媒消息称，上海新世界城已获得《火影忍者》官方授权，将在上海市南京西路上海新世界城11层建设一座《火影忍者》室内主题公园，名为“火影忍者世界”，占地面积达7000平方米。开放日期等其他详细信息还尚未公布。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>这将是《火影忍者》这个大IP在全球的首个主题公园。虽然此前在日本本土举办过该IP的实境展与快闪主题公园，但固定的主题公园还是首个。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>文创行业现有的模式是利用IP进行多种形式的开发，与此同时IP在持续的开发中吸引到不同圈层的用户，放大影响力获得增值。主题公园是IP产业链中的重资产，需要强大的内容支撑。国内主题公园经过快速发展已到一定量级，但其中动漫主题公园并不多。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>华强方特在短短十多年的时间中在全国15个城市建起了24个主题乐园。不过，虽然有《熊出没》IP，但在现有的方特主题乐园中只有部分场景、剧场和舞台剧，并不是实质意义的动漫主题乐园</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>近日，中国主题公园研究院院长林焕杰告诉记者，目前方特的《熊出没》动漫乐园已经完成规划设计在几个城市开建，尚未建成落地。一个热门的IP要有人设丰富的作品、持续的内容、好的平台支撑。除了华强方特，奥飞娱乐、长城动漫也在探索中国动漫主题公园之路。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>在国家政策的推动下，动漫产业产值和主题公园数量激增，但其中仍存在“虚胖”的现象，长效动漫IP和有影响力的主题公园稀缺。<br/>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190405/1554436842310867.jpg\"/><br/><br/>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\"><strong style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\">IP培育期</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>林焕杰认为，中国的主题公园发展可以分为四个时期，经过了2006年开始的快速增长时期后，随着2016年6月16日上海迪士尼乐园开园进入的新时期。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>继上海迪士尼之后，环球影城的主题公园已在北京开工，尼克罗丁频道在中国的首个主题公园正在广东佛山开建，HelloKitty主题公园落户浙江，并将在上海、海口建设新园，默林娱乐集团希望带小猪佩奇主题公园进入中国。还有乐天世界、乐高乐园、东方好莱坞等其他海外知名主题公园纷纷在中国投建或有投建意愿。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>林焕杰指出，国际品牌进入中国之后，对中国主题公园的建设有一定冲击，导致国内一些档次较低、地段不好、管理能力差的主题公园出局。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>在引进的主题公园中，动漫主题乐园占很大一部分。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>动漫与主题公园融合发展模式是动漫产业和旅游业产业融合最直观的模式。动漫资源引入主题公园,进行动漫旅游开发还能克服主题公园对门票价格的限制性,拉长企业的价值链,通过动漫旅游的衍生产品盈利，使现金流更健康。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>林焕杰认为，虽然国内出现了许多主题公园，但主题选择雷同缺乏个性，复制模式居多，没有差异化。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>本土创建的动漫主题公园不少，但许多没有明确的动漫形象主题，如南京月牙湖动漫主题公园、常州环球动漫嬉戏谷、长春多多国动漫主题公园、三亚九龙山动漫主题森林公园、浙江诸暨龙太子欢乐谷动漫主题乐园等。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>国际知名的动漫主题公园一般都是先发展动漫业再延伸至旅游业,当前国内由于缺乏优秀的动漫作品,一般是先建设公园,再寻找动漫主题,边运营边创造属于自己的动漫故事。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>例如常州恐龙园先有主题公园项目，随后延伸至上游主题文化创意及下游动漫与衍生产品制造，陆续推出《恐龙宝贝》系列及《恐龙来了》等动漫剧集和电影以及玩具、礼品等衍生品。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>还有一些是模仿国外的动漫主题。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>江苏省大丰市曾宣布建设以《海贼王》为主题的公园,总投资为5亿元，委托日本木兰创意文化发展株式会社对公园总体形象进行策划和包装，项目招标文件中也指出项目名称是“海贼王动漫主题公园”。但引起版权争议后，项目开发公司出来辟谣称游乐园名称为“大丰港海盗王国游乐园”，与海贼王IP无关。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>作为主题公园规划的基石，国内的优质IP还远远不够，或是停留在动漫和衍生周边产品阶段。当然，国内适用于主题公园的IP不足与动漫IP本身处于用户培育期有关。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>当然，国内发展也不均衡。例如奥飞动漫在PGC领域上，创造了铠甲勇士、巴啦啦小魔仙、超级飞侠、火力少年、开心超人等动漫形象，收购喜洋洋、贝肯熊、功夫料理娘、雷霆战机、魔天记、太极鼠、雏蜂、端脑、镇魂街、十万个冷笑话等多个知名IP。公司旗下拥有原创动力、明星动画、狼烟动画、太极鼠工作室等十余个原创动漫工作室。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>2018年4月，奥飞娱乐出资2750万元，和广东奥睿控股共同投资设立子公司奥飞主题文化科技有限公司，将结合奥飞娱乐旗下IP经营室外实景主题乐园。计划五年内在全国范围内建设多个主题游乐园。其中包括奥飞娱乐与山水文园集团、美国六旗集团联手打造的“超级飞侠”动漫主题公园。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\"><strong style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\">规模“虚胖”</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>对于动漫主题乐园来说，成功与否的先决条件是主题是否足够吸引人“掏腰包”。但传统动漫产业“虚胖”问题凸显，我国动漫行业产值在2018年已突破1500亿元，2014年时才刚突破1000亿元，能拿出手的动漫IP不多。林焕杰也指出，一些主题公园的流量数据存在虚报的现象，投资经营数据失实，误导市场情况严重。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>一个IP建造成主题乐园需要很长时间，短时间内决策投资不利于长效发展。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>林焕杰表示，《哈利·波特》、《加勒比海盗》等都是拍了很多部续集才开始做主题公园。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>“国内还是比较急躁，《熊出没》，《喜羊羊与灰太狼》、《超级飞侠》其实逐渐被认可，把IP变成公园是需要一个很长的过程研发。美国奥兰多迪士尼世界的潘多拉:阿凡达世界主题区，卡梅伦导演用了7年的时间才完成，国内主题公园的筹备建设期往往只有一两年时间，所以受欢迎的程度不高。”林焕杰说道。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>林焕杰还指出，其实也与投资额有很大的关系，国外是投资投入比较大，特别是在设计研发方面，国内的一些项目设施比较粗糙。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>特别是对于动漫主题公园来说，投资成本高昂，但因为受众群体有限，风险或比其它主题公园更大。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>在林焕杰看来，杭州从日本引进的HelloKitty主题公园就做得不好。因为目前动漫公园的主要客群还是儿童，儿童是被动消费群体，有明显的淡旺季。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>“迪士尼也不是纯粹的动漫主题公园，因为覆盖的客户群有限，只能是在大公园里面的一个区域做动漫主题。但是如果是整个的话，游客量是支撑不起来的，没有一个公司可以做好。”林焕杰说，如果是全年龄段的主题公园，才能有一定游客量。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>也就是说，虽然有些动漫IP有特定粉丝群体和较成熟的衍生品市场，短期内聚集人气并不是难事，但生命力是否可持续依然不可知。而且，很多大的IP相对孤立，一个热门IP开发的产品难成系列，不足以提供一个大规模的园区需要，可能会“孤掌难鸣”。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>环球影城创意公司副总裁PaulOsterhout近日接受记者采访时认为，如何衡量IP的投入与产出十分重要，关键在于讲好一个故事并且和主题高度匹配，关注叙事技巧，要简单不能太复杂。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>这对于资金预算较少的主题公园是一个方式。PaulOsterhout表示，主题公园未来将多级发展，超大规模和小规模共同发展。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>“主题公园一方面朝大规模发展，在园区内配套酒店和餐饮；与此同时一些非常小的，基于商业综合体、购物商城的主题公园将会出现，未来将很难区分旅游和购物的界限。”PaulOsterhout向记者指出。</p><p><br/></p>', '1', '0', '0');
INSERT INTO `c5_news` VALUES ('8', '总投资18亿元！韩国乐高乐园预计2022年开业', '核心提示：巨头扎堆韩国，开拓全球市场已成国际品牌商共识。', '李海强', '乐高，主题公园，派拉蒙，游乐园，莫林娱乐', '<p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\">继日本和中国后，韩国成为世界级企业布局颇为频繁的亚太主题公园市场。&nbsp;</span><br/><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span><br/><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><img width=\"600\" height=\"337\" alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190405/1554436939469717.jpg\"/><br/>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>1月7日，韩国当地政府宣布，建在春川的乐高乐园度假区预计2022年开业。该项目总投资为2900亿韩元（18亿元），其中默林娱乐出资2100亿韩元（13亿元），剩余800亿韩元由江原道省政府旗下投资机构LL Development承担。据悉，度假区中的乐高乐园完全归默林娱乐所有和负责运营。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>去年12月，派拉蒙主题公园入驻韩国Inspire综合娱乐度假区，该项目由Mohegan Gaming &amp; Entertainment开发，预计2019年动工，2025年开业。此外，2017年8月，狮门影业宣布第一座室外主题公园狮门电影天地将落户济州神话世界，该乐园占地面积120万平方米，预计2019年开业，是韩国第一个以影视为主题的国际性主题公园。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>游乐园及景点国际协会（IAAPA）近期发布的报告显示，2017年全球主题公园市场规模达到450亿美元，同比增长5%，且未来几年全球近三分之二增长的游客量都来自亚太地区。在各大主题公园运营商、影视、动漫巨头纷纷布局中国市场之际，韩国也成为影视公司和主题公园巨头重点投资对象，原因何在？</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\"><strong style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\">从日本主题公园截取客流？</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>经济比较发达、人均GDP较高以及国际游客较多是外企纷纷布局韩国主题公园市场的主要考量因素。此外，经商环境比较好、韩国人对国际品牌的进入持欢迎态度也是重要因素。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>更重要的是，在中国和日本市场被迪士尼、环球影城等传媒影视巨头占据大部分份额的情况下，综合实力不足的主题公园运营商或影视公司只能另辟新径，或在离大城市比较远的二三线城市，或从周边比较小的国家入手，以“多点开花”的迂回方式获得最大收益。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>很显然，无论是IP品牌比较少的默林娱乐，还是主题公园设计运营不算太强的派拉蒙和狮门影业都属于这一类型的投资者。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>再者，韩国国内与国际主题公园玩家之间的竞争并不算很激烈。在没有迪士尼和环球影城的韩国，默林娱乐的乐高乐园开业后无疑将成为知名度最高的国际主题公园。在韩国国内主题公园中，只有乐山世界和三星爱宝乐园两个大型主题公园，但乐高乐园的全球品牌影响力及丰富的运营经验会让其在竞争中更有底气，而两大影视公司享誉全球的影视IP也会吸引更多游客进入主题公园。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>此外，国际品牌的入场预计能够吸引更多的国内外游客，提振韩国主题公园游客量。<br/>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190405/1554436940557746.jpg\"/><br/>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>《2017年全球景点游客量报告》显示，乐天世界和爱宝乐园2017年游客量分别为670万和630万，虽然在亚太地区均居前十位，但同比分别下降18%和10%。进入区域水上乐园前二十名的水上乐园也出现类似情况，加勒比海湾、江原道海洋世界和熊津娱乐城游客量同比下降分别为3.5%、9.7%和2.1%。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>不过，从积极的角度看，一旦建成更多知名度较高的国际性主题公园，韩国去周边国家游玩日本环球影城或东京迪士尼的游客可能会减少。统计数字显示，2017年赴日国际游客达2870万，同比增长17.5%，其中三分之二增量游客都来自于中国和韩国。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>事实上，这些国际主题公园玩家对进入韩国市场早有准备。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>韩国乐高乐园早在2011年就已经启动，默林娱乐2014年宣布该乐园于2017年开业，但后来因施工中发掘到考古遗址而暂停工程。另外，韩国乐高乐园占地面积接近130万平方米，是日本乐高乐园的两倍，也是全球最大的乐高乐园项目，从项目规模不难看出默林对韩国市场的重视程度。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\"><strong style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\">开拓全球市场已成国际品牌商共识</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>除实力占绝对优势的迪士尼和环球影城外，默林娱乐、六旗娱乐、维亚康姆（派拉蒙母公司）、狮门影业也在主题娱乐领域加紧全球扩张步伐。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>首先，默林娱乐已尝到全球乐高乐园业务扩张为公司带来的甜头。韩国乐高乐园开业后将成为默林娱乐全球第十个、亚洲第三个乐高乐园，公司投资3.5亿美元的纽约乐高乐园也将于2020年开业。CEO尼克瓦尼曾表示，默林娱乐未来计划在全球修建20座乐高乐园，其中至少五座将建在中国。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>财报显示，2017年，默林娱乐全球八个乐高乐园营收6.09亿英镑，同比增长23%，游客量仅为1530万人次，明显比游客量高达4070万人次、营收6.56已英镑的短途景点业务能为公司带来更多利润。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>2018年上半年，在两大业务收入相差无几的情况下，乐高乐园运营利润比短途景点高2000万英镑，默林娱乐对韩国乐高乐园项目投资占比72%的原因也在于此。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>其次，狮门娱乐天地去年以来也开始在全球布局主题公园业务。香港地产商投资的文化娱乐综合体丽新横琴创东方中的狮门娱乐天地将于2019年开业，在西班牙与全球第十大主题公园运营商团聚公园集团合作开发的室内娱乐项目将于2020年开业。2017年9月宣布的美国第一个狮门娱乐城将于2019年在纽约时代广场附近开业。<br/>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190405/1554436940646188.jpg\"/><br/>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>此外，狮门影业还将饥饿游戏等影视IP引入迪拜主题公园度假区，最近还和The Works Entertainment等合作将惊天魔盗团与魔术相结合，推出大型魔术秀在全球进行巡演。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>不过，派拉蒙的全球扩张进程并不顺利。早在2004年，派拉蒙就开始在天津考察计划修建主题公园，预计投资70亿美元，但最后据传项目没有通过审批。2015年，派拉蒙在华南地区的广州或深圳修建主题公园的选址消息至今没有下文。2017年，派拉蒙在西班牙的主题公园项目因涉及生态保护问题而未获得当地政府批准，同年6月退出英国伦敦包含派拉蒙主题公园的32亿英镑度假区项目。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>派拉蒙（维亚康姆）在中国落地的项目也有所增加。2015年5月，派拉蒙与河北迁安政府签订计划修建包括派拉蒙主题公园在内的多功能城市文化旅游综合体。去年12月，以维亚康姆旗下另一IP为主题的全球最大尼克室内主题乐园宣布落户重庆，预计2020年开业。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>在过去的2018年，迪士尼713亿美元收购21世纪福克斯、电信巨头AT&amp;T 850亿美元收购时代华纳交易限制被解除、康卡斯特390亿美元收购天空广播公司三大交易将对未来的主题公园行业格局产生深远的影响。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>虽然全球扩张速度比较快，但默林娱乐对主题公园的投资持冷静态度，其CEO尼克瓦尼曾表示，从主题公园行业赚的钱并不容易，因为投资周期非常长。不过，在迪士尼收购福克斯变得更加强大后，作为全球第二的默林娱乐需要在全球扩张的同时考虑进行更多并购壮大实力，以避免与迪士尼之间的差距进一步拉大。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>而对于处于全球扩张中的派拉蒙和狮门影业来说，维亚康姆与CBS合并，甚至有业内人士认为，狮门影业与两大公司合并或许是更好的选择。这种交易不仅能够为各方带来更多的影视资源，还可以将众多IP品牌引入主题公园或以各种主题娱乐形式展示。毕竟，找到实力雄厚的靠山对在主题公园行业中获得更多的优质内容资源和打造强大的流量平台尤为重要。</p><p><br/></p>', '0', '35', '0');
INSERT INTO `c5_news` VALUES ('9', '引流能力堪比迪士尼！迪拜全球村带给国内景区什么启示？', '核心提示：迪拜控股旗下阿拉伯传媒集团近日宣布，第23届迪拜全球村开业两个月游客量超过300万。迪拜全球村（Dubai\'s Global Village）是集家庭购物、娱乐、旅游、度假于一体的多元文化节日公园，占地面积160万平方米，每年运营', '李海强', '迪士尼，迪拜全球村，游乐园，旅游', '<p>迪拜控股旗下阿拉伯传媒集团近日宣布，第23届迪拜全球村开业两个月游客量超过300万。<br/>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;<img width=\"600\" height=\"400\" alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190405/1554437079734255.jpg\"/><br/>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>迪拜全球村（Dubai&#39;s Global Village）是集家庭购物、娱乐、旅游、度假于一体的多元文化节日公园，占地面积160万平方米，每年运营时间为11月到次年4月。第23届迪拜全球村于去年10月30日开始，今年4月7日结束。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>两个月游客量超过300万是什么概念？2017年，迪士尼全球游客量最高的是神奇王国主题公园，共接待2045万游客。以全年运营计算，每月平均接待170万游客。整个华特迪士尼世界四个主题公园平均月游客量仅为116万。全球村的引流能力可见一斑。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>那么，迪拜全球村到底有何特别之处，平均每年吸引全球500多万游客前来游玩？</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\"><strong style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\">一、三大运营措施吸引全球游客</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>在1996年开办的第一年，全球村只是迪拜河附近出售世界各地产品的摊贩聚集地，但现在该场所已成为全球最吸引人流的家庭购物、文化、旅游、休闲、娱乐度假目的地。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>露天室外游乐场，包括烟花、音乐会、杂技等娱乐及表演节目，每个参展国家的产品工艺品，以及来自世界各地的美食，是全球村成为中东甚至全球网红打卡地的四大特色。<br/>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190405/1554437079334104.jpg\"/></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>数据显示，第22届迪拜全球村游客量超过600万人次，汇集来自全球75个国家的10000多个展商，交易额达29亿迪拉姆（8亿美元），同比增长26%。第21届全球村从2016年11月到2017年4月8日，在159天运营时间内共接待560万游客，同比增长5%，交易额为23亿迪拉姆（6.3亿美元）。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>为了吸引游客，运营商主要采用以下几大措施，以提供更好的产品、服务及体验。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><strong style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\">1、不断更新升级产品，提升游客体验</strong></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>根据游客的需求不断更新设施、增加新景点及提升游客体验，是全球村成功的关键。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>在新一届活动中，运营商对最受游客欢迎的嘉年华（Carnival）露天游乐场设施进行更新升级，不仅增加6个骑乘设施及100个电子游戏项目，还大幅增加游戏区的面积。最新一届活动还推出VIP套餐，新增嘉年华游乐场马戏团表演以及整个公园23个餐厅打折优惠项目。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>2017年2月，全球村运营商与愤怒的小鸟持有者达成协议，获得品牌在全球村的两年授权，用于实景演出及非门票表演节目。此外，全球村运营商还与Green Gold Animation达成合作，将印度街机游戏项目Chhota Bheem引入全球村。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>在19届活动中，宝莱坞表演节目Viva Bollywood大获成功，运营商总结经验，在20届全球村活动中推出Viva Bollywood II，并采用全部来自孟买的印度人表演团队。<br/>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190405/1554437079750457.jpg\"/></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>目前，游客进出全球村平均仅需9分钟，即便在周末、法定节假日和音乐会期间也是如此，即便号称世界上最快乐地方的加州迪士尼乐园可能也达不到这一效率。而游客体验改观的主要原因是，运营商在新一季活动之前大大改善及升级基础设施，对游客经过的8个步行桥进行翻修，去年还修建了新的文化广场和类似迪士尼大道的全球村大道。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>客流管控能力也是游客良好体验的重要保证。迪拜全球村现有18300个停车位，比加州迪士尼乐园已有Mickey &amp; Friends 1万多个停车位与在建的6000多个停车位之和还要多，仅从这一个方面可以看出这项活动的庞大客流及运营方对客流管控的重视程度。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><strong style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\">2、与迪拜购物节协同，多措并举提升游客参与感</strong></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>在第23届活动期间，全球村周边的迪拜购物节推出2018年12月26日到2019年1月27日的促销活动，每周一次的抽奖活动在迪拜全球村的主舞台现场直播，每年接待300万游客的购物节为全球村导入巨大客流。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>除酒店、娱乐、邮轮、甜点等代金券奖品外，全球村每周还将抽出赢得10万、5万和三个1万迪拉姆现金的游客，这对于大多数花费15迪拉姆门票的游客来说，在购物中心消费200迪拉姆便获得一次抽奖机会无疑具有强大的吸引力。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>再如，2016年，迪拜购物节主办方与珠宝公司Jumbo Electronics合作完成世界上最大的黄金展示，展示的黄金重250公斤，价值高达3500万迪拉姆（960万美元）。更有幸运游客赢得价值2.5万迪拉姆（6850美元）的纯金索尼PlayStation 4 电子<a style=\"color: rgb(34, 85, 136); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; text-decoration: underline; word-break: break-all;\" href=\"https://www.ctoy.com.cn/sell/list-146.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong class=\"keylink\" style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-weight: 400; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 3px; padding-right: 3px; padding-top: 0px; word-break: break-all;\">游戏机</strong></a>。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>去年全球村组织180位厨师花费12个小时准备5000升卡拉克茶创下世界纪录，并将其免费供给5万游客使用。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>此外，周一推出的妇女及家庭专场也吸引大批本地及来自全球各地的游客，很多国外旅行者为了参与全球村活动甚至把度假时间推迟几个月。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><strong style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\">3、文化演出及明星音乐会成引流主力</strong></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>第23届全球村有历史上最大的演出阵容。登台演出的100多名专业表演者从阿联酋、英国、乌克兰、哥伦比亚、印度、中国等全球各地3000名表演者中选出。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>全球村运营商表示，在每年平均500左右的游客量中，55%的游客来全球村体验娱乐及演出项目，公司每次活动在这两方面的开支大约为540万美元。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>2017年，第22届全球村在159天的运营时间内共提供1.2万场文化、娱乐等表演节目。其中，阿拉伯及国际明星在该公园进行的演出超过20场。<br/>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190405/1554437080224284.jpg\"/></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>明星效应带来巨大客流是吸引游客的重要手段。比如2018年12月28日，埃及歌手默罕默德-哈曼基在迪拜全球村举办音乐会，游客数突破13万人，创历史新高。12月31日，迪拜全球村跨年活动接待了11万多名游客。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>此外，第23届活动开始不久后，全球村还邀请宝莱坞影星沙鲁克汗参加，这无疑会吸引不少以印度游客为主的消费人群。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\"><strong style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\">二、打造全球品牌走向世界</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>迪拜度假村从一开始的定位就是吸引国际化客群，进行国际化运营，具有成为国际性品牌和国际性企业的基因。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>1997年，只有18个国家在迪拜全球村参展，不过这一数字在2018年已增至78个。其游客量也从第一年的50万增至2012年顶峰时期的700万。此外，从2013年到2018年，全球村的参展商从3000多个增至10000个。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>目前，迪拜全球村运营人员共有10000个，但全职运营人员只有50人，3000个来自阿联酋周边国际，其余7000人自来全球其他地方。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>迪拜旅游局统计数据显示，印度、沙特和英国是迪拜2017年前三大国际客源市场，游客量分别为210万、150万和130万，中国以76.4万游客排名第五，俄罗斯游客增至212%至53万，排名第八。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>迪拜旅游局负责人表示，在2017年所有国际游客中，以休闲度假为目的游客占比73.8%，而商旅客占比仅为11.5%。很显然，迪拜全球村、迪拜主题公园等大型景点都从国际市场看到巨大商机，采取各项措施吸引国际游客。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>在第22届全球村活动后，迪拜全球村运营商宣布，全球村中最重要的露天游乐场将不再与其他企业合作，而是由自己独立运营。公司计划借此机会打造新的品牌，推出独特产品，持续引入新的<a style=\"color: rgb(34, 85, 136); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; text-decoration: underline; word-break: break-all;\" href=\"http://rides.ctoy.com.cn/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong class=\"keylink\" style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-weight: 400; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 3px; padding-right: 3px; padding-top: 0px; word-break: break-all;\">游乐设施</strong></a>为游客带来全新体验。而这背后更大的目的，是将全球村这一活动推广至全球。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>据全球村负责人介绍，公司在打造全球村全球品牌和购买版权方面已投入6800万美元。未来计划通过全球村品牌将自己创作的杂技表演、百老汇式音乐剧、街头娱乐及儿童舞台剧输出到世界各地。目前在谈的两个国家是印度和沙特阿拉伯。<br/>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20190405/1554437080206953.png\"/></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Mi