; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>据全球村负责人介绍，公司在打造全球村全球品牌和购买版权方面已投入6800万美元。未来计划通过全球村品牌将自己创作的杂技表演、百老汇式音乐剧、街头娱乐及儿童舞台剧输出到世界各地。目前在谈的两个国家是印度和沙特阿拉伯。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>迪拜全球村CEO Ahmad Hussain Bin Essa 表示，全球村并没有把自己定位为主题公园，所以没有引入过山车项目。“我们自己的定位是露天游乐场，向游客提供类似美国康尼岛游乐城或德国慕尼黑啤酒节的体验，并将光、电、音乐、骑乘等体验植入游乐环境中。”</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>全球村运营商并不担心来自迪拜或其他阿联酋周边地区的竞争，迪拜强大的国际游客量足以容纳更多的旅游娱乐景点。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>一方面，迪拜2017年接待1780万国际游客，到2020年预计吸引2000万游客。另一方面，Alpen Capital最近的一份报告显示，阿联酋地区的游客在过去的十年里在以12%的速度增长，而国际游客人数每年平均增速仅为5%。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>该运营商甚至认为，尽管全球村游客量高于附近全年运营的IMG Worlds of Aventure等主题公园，但两类景点之间是互补，而不纯粹是竞争的关系。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>Essa认为，迪拜吸引游客成为旅游目的地有四大驱动因素，其中，星级酒店和有国际影响力的餐饮品牌，以及强大的交通运输网络都具备可持续特点，而休闲娱乐作为第四大因素，则能够促使迪拜修建更多的乐园和景点，打造新的目的地，从而带动更多的需求。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>公司近期计划是，与全球村概念设计公司Sanderson合作打造升级版的游乐场，还计划探索设计出便于在全球各地进行运输的游乐设施。不过，其未来与附近的主题公园IMG Worlds of Adventure、娱乐综合体迪拜乐园、体育城、迪拜国际城等旅游胜地是相互引流还是相互竞争，尚需时间检验。&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\"><strong style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\">三、全球村运营模式给国内景区的三大启示</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>迪拜全球村的成功或许能给目前严重依赖门票收入的国内景区或主题乐园一些启示。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>第一，不断更新基础设施或引入新的产品业态，提升游客体验。很多景区进入之后给游客的感觉是空空荡荡，或者千篇一律，同质化严重。迪拜全球村模仿迪士尼，修建文化广场和全球村大道就是为了给游客留下特别的记忆。迪士尼在门前的米老鼠等迎客吉祥物就要花费数十万美元，打造吸引人眼球景点的重要性不言而喻。此外，每年引进新的马戏、特技、娱乐等演出也大大丰富公园的产品业态。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>第二，跨界寻找优质合伙伙伴。在当今文旅融合成为潮流之际，娱乐、零售、地产等与旅游的结合越来越密切。景区或主题公园应积极与附近能拉动流量的品牌商或节日活动结合在一起联合营销，打造更多的“明星”项目。在160万平米的场地上，全球村举办1.2万场表演，除运营商邀请的大型文化演出或明星音乐会外，引入大量各显其能的特色演出也值得国内景区或主题公园借鉴。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>第三，展示文化多样性吸引更多的消费群体。作为多元文化节日公园，全球村吸引全球近百个不同民族的商家在展示商品、美食和工艺品的同时，也吸引游客体验不同国家的传统文化，极大激发游客体验不同国家特色的积极性。虽然国内大部分景区或主题公园还谈不上国际化，但从这个想法出发，至少可以引入不同民族、不同区域的特色节日、文化、工艺品、美食，形成差异化的竞争策略。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>当然，迪拜全球村至今已有20多年的历史，地域不同，消费者的消费观念不同，企业的营销方式和预算也不相同，一些成功的运营思路在国内不一定通用。但可以肯定的是，主题公园或景区应根据自身消费群体喜好，提供符合游客需求且差异化的产品，提升游客的游玩体验和消费频次</p><p><br/></p>', '1', '0', '0');
INSERT INTO `c5_news` VALUES ('10', '迪拜主题公园度假区2018年游客近280万人次，中国俄罗斯暴增', '核心提示：中东地区主题公园市场或已饱和？', '李海强', '主题公园，乐高乐园', '<p>1月14日，中东最大主题公园运营商DXB Entertainments 宣布旗下迪拜主题公园度假区2018年游客量接近280万人次，同比增长22%。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>数据显示，迪拜主题公园2018年第四季度接待81.9万游客，创单个季度游客量最高纪录，较去年同期的79.6万增长3%。公司称，最后一个季度游客量实现增长主要得益于冬季活动比较多，适逢万圣节、阿联酋成立47周年纪念日、学生寒假和法定节假日等。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>此外，度假区内唯一酒店Lapita第四季度的入住率为63%，12月中有几天的酒店入住率一度达到100%。 从整个2018年来看，酒店的平均入住率上升至60%，较去年同期的35%提升二十五个百分点。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>公司公告显示，迪拜主题公园2018年取得良好业绩的原因在于，度假区多个主题公园的年票整合工作卓有成效，酒店入住率提升，由此入住酒店的客人和国际游客数量得以增加。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\"><strong style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\">中国俄罗斯游客暴增</strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>DXB Entertainments CEO兼董事总经理Mohamed Almulla表示，迪拜主题公园游客量增长22%，国际游客增长40%，这说明公司与阿联酋航空、迪拜道路交通管理局（RTA）、迪拜机场及中国银联签订的合作协议效果初显。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>他进一步表示，公司2019年的主要目标是，继续增加国际游客数量，这类消费群体是度假区增长的主要推动力。同时，保持本地和周边海湾地区强大的游客基数也至关重要。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>迪拜的长期目标是，到2025年吸引2300-2500万国际游客。毫无疑问，迪拜主题公园计划借此机会吸引更多的国际游客。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>财报显示，2018年上半年，迪拜主题公园国际游客占度假区总游客量的38%，主要来自中东北非、海湾国家及印度次大陆。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>但中国的中产阶级、俄罗斯等也是其重点营销对象。统计数字显示，2018年上半年，中国游客增长9%至45.3万，俄罗斯游客暴增74%至40.3万。2017年中国赴迪拜旅游游客以76.4万排名第五。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>迪拜2017年接待1580万国际游客，同比增长6.2%，计划到2020年达到2000万的目标。在保证本地和周边国家游客稳步增长的同时，DXB Entertainments千方百计吸引迅速增长的国际游客进入主题公园便不足为奇。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\"><strong style=\"font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; word-break: break-all;\">中东主题公园市场已饱和？</strong></span></span></p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>迪拜主题公园度假区目前占地面积230公顷，总投资36亿美元，是中东地区最大的综合性度假休闲目的地。度假区以宝莱坞、好莱坞及乐高乐园三大主题公园及乐高水上乐园为明星项目。乐高主题酒店和迪拜六旗乐园正在修建中，原计划2019年底开业。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>DXB Entertainments是迪拜主题公园度假区的母公司，2014年在迪拜金融市场（DFM）上市。除度假区外，DXB Entertainments还负责管理迪拜6家短途景点以及迪拜政府开发商Meraas旗下的多个电影院。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>公司开业第一年的游客量目标是670万，但2017年仅有230万游客入园。2017年公司全年亏损11.2亿迪拉姆（3.04亿美元）。去年3月，公司与多个债权人达成11.4亿美元的债务重组协议。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>去年11月，在第三季度财报电话会议上，公司透露董事会正在重新评估正在修建的六旗乐园，投资达7亿美元的扩建项目开业日期可能推迟。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>公司表示，对项目进行战略性审查的目的是，根据现有的客户需求重新考量六旗乐园项目的规模、修建进度及可能的替代方案，并称该决定可能会对迪拜六旗乐园之前预定的开业日期造成影响。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>运营商DXB Entertainmetns计划规划的迪拜六旗乐园中打造世界上最大的过山车，度假区目前共有27个骑乘设施或景点。项目于2016年开始动工，预计2019年开业。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>近年来，中东地区主题公园市场异常火爆，多个大型主题公园项目纷纷。除迪拜主题公园度假区外，还有阿布扎比法拉利世界、迪拜IMG冒险世界、阿布扎比华纳兄弟世界等。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>正在修建的主题公园项目还包括IMG冒险世界附近的二期项目IMG传奇世界、预计2022年开业的阿布扎比海洋世界。去年4月，迪拜福克斯世界开发商因担心这一地区主题公园过剩而宣布停止继续开发项目。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>值得注意的是，除迪拜主题公园外，其他所有项目都位于阿联酋地区阿布扎比的亚斯岛。虽然岛上的法拉利世界、IMG冒险世界、华纳兄弟世界、亚斯水上乐园，以及即将开业的IMG传奇世界和海洋世界会产生一定程度的内部竞争，但整体而言，交通及气候占优势的亚斯岛对游客的吸引力要由于迪拜主题公园度假区。</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;,Tahoma,Verdana,Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 32px; -ms-text-size-adjust: auto; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px;\"></span></p><p>想要成为中东地区第一大主题公园，DXB Entertainments在营销、运营等能力仍需进一步提升。</p><p><br/></p>', '0', '0', '0');
